NIGERIAN Afro-fusion Flowkits is still basking in the glory of his debut Extended Play (EP) entitled, Versatile. The project which was released last year as continue to generate positive reviews from fans and pundits. Speaking on the success of the EP, the Pop rapper/singer said he will continue to set high standards.”I’m setting a standard for my musical career as I have plans of working with the big guns in the music industry. My debut EP, Versatile has increased my fanbase who are strongly rooting for my talent,” the Humbrella Beatz singer said. “Following the release of my body of work in 2020. The EP has been doing really good on music stores and the name Flowkits is spreading like wide fire, raking thousands of streams and commendations on the internet.”